Private Events
Host your event with us
With a direct view of our exclusive small batch brewhouse, the La Sétima Lounge features a private 12-tap bar, free Wi-Fi, and is ADA accessible. The Lounge accommodates up to 40 guests for a seated dinner or 75 for a mix & mingle celebration. This room is the perfect spot for private dinners, happy hours, bridal/baby showers, lectures, wine/beer tastings, and much more.
